title: Cancer and Food Avaliability Analysis
description: We did an exploratory analysis of cancer rates and food avaliability (a proxy for food consumption) in the US in search of a relationship between the two.

title: Recipe and Ratings Analysis
description: We did an analysis on how the cooktime of a recipe impacted its rating, from over 1000 recipes from Food.com, and built a classifier to predict the amount of time a given recipe would take.
